{
  "stem": "20575.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's-- after that, you know, we were put-- we were-- went back, back to the barracks and back to work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one day in-- I think it was end of March, they, they gathered us together from the barracks, line up, and got us to cattle wagons again, put us in there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't know where they wanted to bring us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Later, we heard they want us-- to bring us to the main camp, which-- Flossenburg, that was full.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because there, they still-- there, I saw heaps of dead people lying there when we-- when we go-- went through.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were on the road, on the-- on the train for at least maybe, maybe two or three weeks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They didn't know where to bring us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And what they did in-between, they loosened up the, the-- you know, they opened up the train, disconnected it, and put, put other trains in-between with soldiers and with ammunitions because it was kind of a camouflage.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because the fight, they were-- constantly were planes going, fighting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I remember we had those little things where we got our soups in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was like metal-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I wouldn't say that's a plate.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But we used to put this on our head.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We were hoping, like, this would help us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so in-between, we were going-- we were going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We went through Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I remember we stopped in Pilsen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because we didn't get anything to eat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I remember we got, like-- in that plate, we got a, a, a, a little bit soup of something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I tell you, they didn't know where, where to bring us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We were hoping, since we saw we were in Czechoslovakia, that they might bring us back to Terezin.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But they didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
